  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an immediate action, you briefly shield the target from harm using their own blood. The target suffers blood loss and gains a number of temporary hit points equal to the blood loss plus your casting ability modifier which lasts until the start of the target&#8217;s next turn. An unwilling creature may attempt a Fortitude saving throw to negate this effect. You may spend a spell point to increase the temporary hit points granted by an amount equal to your caster level and DR/&#8211; equal to the blood loss until the start of the target&#8217;s next turn.</p>\n",
